title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 §§ 296-1.11 - Parking in other facilities
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 §§ 296-1.11 - Parking in other facilities

State Regulations

Unless approval is received from the Bureau of Parking

Services, a permit holder may only park in the OGS parking facility to which
they have been specifically assigned. Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9
§§
296-1.11

State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
